#. Plugin Name of the plugin
#: nudge.php
msgid "Nudge - Free Shipping Progress Bar for WooCommerce"
msgstr "Nudge - pasek postępu do darmowej dostawy dla WooCommerce"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin
#: nudge.php
msgid "https://plogins.com/nudge/"
msgstr "https://plogins.com/nudge/"

#. Description of the plugin
#: nudge.php
msgid ""
"Show a free-shipping progress bar that nudges shoppers to add more to their "
"cart."
msgstr ""
"Pokaż pasek postępu do darmowej dostawy, który zachęca klientów do dodania "
"większej liczby produktów do koszyka."

#. Author of the plugin
#: nudge.php
msgid "WPPoland"
msgstr "WPPoland"

#. Author URI of the plugin
#: nudge.php
msgid "https://plogins.com/"
msgstr "https://plogins.com/"

#: nudge.php:47
msgid ""
"Nudge - Free Shipping Progress Bar for WooCommerce requires WooCommerce to "
"be active."
msgstr ""
"Nudge - pasek postępu do darmowej dostawy dla WooCommerce wymaga aktywnego "
"WooCommerce."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:41
msgid "Nudge: Free Shipping Bar"
msgstr "Nudge: pasek darmowej dostawy"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:42
msgid "Nudge"
msgstr "Nudge"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:103
msgid ""
"Nudge shows customers how close they are to free shipping and exactly how "
"much more to add to unlock it. It updates live as the cart changes. The "
"defaults work out of the box, adjust below only if you want to."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:110
msgid "General"
msgstr "Ogólne"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:111
msgid ""
"Turn the bar on and choose where shoppers see it. Showing it on both cart "
"and checkout keeps the goal in front of them through the whole purchase."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:115
msgid "Enable Nudge"
msgstr "Włącz Nudge"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:119
msgid "Show the free-shipping progress bar to shoppers."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:121
msgid ""
"When off, the bar and its assets never load, no styles or scripts are added "
"to the front end."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:125
msgid "Cart page"
msgstr "Strona koszyka"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:125
msgid "Show the bar on the cart page, above the totals."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:126
msgid "Checkout page"
msgstr "Strona zamówienia"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:126
msgid "Show the bar on checkout, so the goal stays visible while they pay."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:133
msgid "Free-shipping threshold"
msgstr "Próg darmowej dostawy"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:134
msgid ""
"Where the “you reach free shipping at…” amount comes from. Automatic keeps "
"the bar in sync with your real shipping rules, so it is never wrong after a "
"price change."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:139
msgid "Threshold source"
msgstr "Źródło progu"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:146
msgid "Automatic (from free-shipping method)"
msgstr "Automatyczne (z metody darmowej dostawy)"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:147
msgid "Manual (fixed amount)"
msgstr "Ręczne (stała kwota)"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:156
msgid ""
"Automatic reads the minimum order amount from your WooCommerce free-shipping "
"method, the smallest one across your shipping zones, so the bar updates "
"itself when you change that rule. The manual amount below is used as a "
"fallback when no such method is found."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:161
msgid "Manual amount"
msgstr "Kwota ręczna"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:165
msgid ""
"In your store currency, before shipping and taxes. Used when the source is "
"Manual, or as the fallback for Automatic. Default: 50."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:173
msgid "Messages"
msgstr "Komunikaty"

#. translators: %s: the {amount} token, shown as a styled chip.
#: src/Admin/Settings.php:178
#, php-format
msgid ""
"What the bar says before and after the goal is reached. Write %s where you "
"want the remaining amount, it is replaced with the value formatted in your "
"store currency (e.g. $12.00)."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:187
msgid "Progress message"
msgstr "Komunikat postępu"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:192 src/Admin/Settings.php:204
msgid "Shoppers see:"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:199
msgid "Success message"
msgstr "Komunikat sukcesu"

#: templates/progress-bar.php:42
msgid "Progress towards free shipping"
msgstr "Postęp do darmowej dostawy"

